Package: sampafeatures
Title: Assign articulatory features to X-SAMPA characters
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rasmus", "Puggaard-Rode", , "r.puggaard@phonetik.uni-muenchen.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4522-9987"))
Description: Adds columns with articulatory features to a data frame based on phonetic transcription 
    using X-SAMPA. Default articulatory features are already defined, but the user can also add 
    non-standard X-SAMPA characters or change the default feature values.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
URL: https://github.com/rpuggaardrode/sampafeatures
BugReports: https://github.com/rpuggaardrode/sampafeatures/issues
Imports: 
    dplyr, stringr
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
